title: Excalibur WoW Burning Crusade 2.4.3 - With Basic AddOns
description:
ExcaliburWoW - The Burning Crusade

For everyone who wants to experience the pre-wotlk era, in a blizzlike way!
Create a free account at http://www.excalibur-wow.com/ and join today.

Server description:
Sick of Pandaria, Cataclysm or Wrath of the Lich King, in search for the good old TBC content? Or sick of unstable servers? Search no more! This is one of the most blizzlike TBC servers existing for 5 years, located in the USA, no rollbacks, no game breaking bugs no latency issues! 

XP rates: x2 
Drop rates: x1 
Money rates: x1 

Friendly Game Masters who can assist you via gmhelp channel at all times, fun events and great community! Everyone is welcome to join our WoW community, Hope to see you soon!
